definitions.definition: A series of links united; a series or order of things depending on each other, as if linked together; a chain , a succession .
The application of these series of links.
The operation of joining multiple character strings .
A character string formed by joining multiple character strings .

main_definition: ( countable ) A series of links united; a series or order of things depending on each other, as if linked together; a chain , a succession .
secondary_definitions: ( uncountable ) The application of these series of links.
( programming ) The operation of joining multiple character strings .
( programming ) A character string formed by joining multiple character strings .
